Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: KSBA - Santa Barbara Municipal Airport
Description: The airport next to UCSB, a convenient spot if people want to have a aerial tour of the shoreline.

Name: KLAX - Los Angeles International Airport
Description: The third busiest airport in the world! Los Angeles International Airport, commonly referred to as LAX, locates on the west coast of the U.S..

Name: ZBAA - Beijing Capital International Airport
Description: One of the two major international airports in Beijing. It is the busiest airport in Asia.

Name: ZBAD - Beijing Daxing International Airport
Description: The other major international airport in Beijing. It has the world's largest single-building airport terminal.

Name: PANC - Ted Stevens Anchorage International Airport
Description: Ted Stevens Anchorage International Airport is the fifteh busiest cargo airport in the world. It also served as a stop for trans-pacific flights during the Cold War.
